  <brief_title>Gut Oxygenation and Laparoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>GUT OXYGENATION DURING AND AFTER LAPAROSCOPIC AND OPEN COLON RESECTION. A RANDOMIZAD CLINICAL TRIAL</official_title>
